{"id": "wdt_dml_wdt_init", "label": "init()", "source_file": "wdt_dml/wdt.dml", "source_location": "L651", "signature": "method init()", "doc": "Device initialization: sets the counter and all state variables to their power-on defaults (device unlocked, clock assumed enabled, output signals low)."}
